narration_text: #C C serves pancake from a plate to another.
#C C puts chop sticks on the table.
#C C servers pancake from pan to plate with a spatula.
#C C puts spatula on the pan.
#C C puts plate with pancake in micro wave.
#C C covers plate with another plate.
#C C picks #unsure in a glass plate.
#C C adds #unsure to the pancake with chop sticks.
#C C puts glass plate on the table.
#C C puts glass chop sticks down.
#C C adds coriander on the pancake.
#C C puts piece of clothing on the table.
#C C pulls out plate with pancake.
#C C adds pancake to a plate.
#C C puts plate on the sink.
#C C adds #unknown to pancake with chop sticks.
#C C adds coriander to pancake chop sticks.
